    "title": "Generating a signature for attributable web ads"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A user’s device calls the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.skadnetworkforwebads/documentation/SKAdNetworkforWebAds/Get-a-signed-SKAdNetwork-ad-payload-for-a-web-ad.",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " endpoint on your server when a user taps the web ad that you create using the instructions in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.skadnetworkforwebads/documentation/SKAdNetworkforWebAds/creating-an-attributable-ad-link",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". To respond to the request, you need to provide the values in the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.skadnetworkforwebads/documentation/SKAdNetworkforWebAds/AdImpressionResponse",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", which includes a cryptographic signature.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To generate the signature, combine the required values from the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.skadnetworkforwebads/documentation/SKAdNetworkforWebAds/signature",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " object and cryptographically sign the resulting string. Use the ad network ID and PKCS#8 private key that you establish when registering to use the API. For more information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/StoreKit/registering-an-ad-network",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Combine-the-parameters",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Combine the parameters",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Create the UTF-8 string using the required ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.skadnetworkforwebads/documentation/SKAdNetworkforWebAds/signature",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " object parameters.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "Lowercase the string representation of the nonce from the ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.skadnetworkforwebads/documentation/SKAdNetworkforWebAds/signature",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": " object. Failing to do so results in an invalid signature. Only ads with valid signatures can get ad attributions.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Important",
          "style": "important",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Combine the values into a UTF-8 string with an invisible separator (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "‘\\u2063’",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ") between them, in the exact order the code below shows:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "version + '\\u2063' + ad_network_id + '\\u2063' + source_identifier + '\\u2063' + itunes_item_id + '\\u2063' + nonce + '\\u2063' + source_domain + '\\u2063' + fidelity_type + '\\u2063' + timestamp"
          ],
          "syntax": "c",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Sign-the-combined-string",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Sign the combined string",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Sign the combined UTF-8 string with the following key and algorithm:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Your PKCS#8 private key.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Elliptic Curve Digital Signature Algorithm (ECDSA) with a SHA-256 hash.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The resulting Digital Encoding Rules (DER)-formatted binary value is the signature.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Encode-the-signature",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Encode the signature",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Encode the binary signature you generate into a Base64 string. The result is your ad network attribution signature. The signature string should look similar to the following:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "MEQCIEQlmZRNfYzKBSE8QnhLTIHZZZWCFgZpRqRxHss65KoFAiAJgJKjdrWdkLUOCCjuEx2RmFS7daRzSVZRVZ8RyMyUXg=="
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For more information about Base64 encoding, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/data/2142853-base64encodedstring",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Use-the-generated-signature-string",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Use the generated signature string",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "After you generate the signature, use this value in the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "signature",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " parameter of the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.skadnetworkforwebads/documentation/SKAdNetworkforWebAds/AdImpressionResponse",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". If the user installs and launches the advertised app, the attribution-winning ad network receives an install-validation postback. For more information about postbacks, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/StoreKit/verifying-an-install-validation-postback",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
